","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"event84-06-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"마리나","body":"으, 응……\n오늘은 다른 스태프가 대신 해줬거든.\n긴장해서 일할 상황이 아닐 거라면서.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event84-06-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"마리나","body":"설마 스스로도 이렇게까지 긴장할 줄은 몰랐어……\n내가 예전에 만든 노래를 다른 사람이 연주하게 되다니\n그런 경험은 지금까지 없으니까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event84-06-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"유키나","body":"후후……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event84-06-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"마리나","body":"응? 왜 그래, 유키나 짱?\n내, 내가 무슨 이상한 말이라도 했어?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"surpri